WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.518
By the end of this module, you will be able to do five

00:00:04.568 --> 00:00:09.086
things. First, create effective video updates that inform customers and lift approval of

00:00:09.136 --> 00:00:13.654
recommended work. Second, use text messaging professionally and appropriately with Porsche customers.

00:00:13.704 --> 00:00:18.222
Third, write clear, professional emails when you need a written record.

00:00:18.272 --> 00:00:22.790
Fourth, choose the right channel based on the message and the customer.

00:00:22.840 --> 00:00:27.358
And fifth, avoid the common digital mistakes that quietly erode your professionalism.
